item.title: Blue Jay Pizza
item.description: Don’t worry, today’s brand new story is NOT about a pizza that has birds as a topping, but it’s still suitably weird. Written by an 8 year old from New York named Jolee. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/GLT5781983979

item.title: The vital question Taskrabbit founder Leah Solivan wished she asked investors
item.description: A pioneer in the gig economy, Leah Solivan joins host Jeff Berman to share scale lessons from founding Taskrabbit. Hear how a need for dog food on a snowy night grew into a global business acquired by IKEA. She also reveals how her experience as an entrepreneur is shaping her next act as an early-stage investor. Leah has a new podcast of her own in the works: Breaking Precedent Read a transcript of this episode: https://mastersofscale... Feed: https://rss.art19.com/masters-of-scale
